Competitive Play Framework

Project overview branch for the Competitive Play Framework mod.

Purpose:
- Keep a dedicated branch that explains the mod at a high level
- Serve as the base branch for the Competitive Play Framework working branches

Child branches:
- CPF-Main: stable/published line
- CPF-Dev: active development line

Notes:
- This branch is intentionally lightweight
- It acts as the project root for Competitive Play Framework in this repository layout
